#: holidaycategories.cpp:77
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Public Holiday: a day-off from work or school (typically) to commemorate a "
"historical event, or to honor people.  Public holidays are always bounded to "
"a political region at national, regional or local level."
msgstr ""
"Festiu oficial: un dia de descans de la feina o l'escola (normalment) per a "
"commemorar un esdeveniment històric o per honrar persones.  Els dies festius "
"estan sempre lligats a una regió política a nivell nacional, regional o "
"local."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:82
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Civil Service Holiday: a day-off from work for government workers but not a "
"day off for private sector workers."
msgstr ""
"Festiu públic: un dia lliure de treball per als treballadors del govern, "
"però no un dia lliure per als treballadors del sector privat."

# skip-rule: kct-range
#: holidaycategories.cpp:85
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Religious Holiday: a special day in a religion and not bound to any "
"political region. Religions can have holidays that range in devotion to "
"those were work/school are forbidden, days of prayer obligation, to "
"historical remembrances, etc. Governments often have public holidays for "
"some religious holidays."
msgstr ""
"Festiu religiós: un dia especial en una religió i no lligat a cap regió "
"política. Les religions poden tenir festius que van des de la devoció a les "
"que estan prohibides la feina/escola, dies d'obligació de pregària, a "
"records històrics, etc. Els governs sovint tenen dies festius per a algunes "
"festivitats religioses."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:91
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"School Holiday: a day-off from school, either as a one-off Public Holiday or "
"extended periods between school terms.  This can vary widely depending on "
"school level, type, location."
msgstr ""
"Vacances escolars: un dia lliure d'escola, ja sigui com a vacances públiques "
"puntuals o períodes prolongats entre trimestres escolars.  Això pot variar "
"força depenent del nivell escolar, tipus, ubicació."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:96
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Government Holiday: a special day recognized by a political region but "
"without a day-off for workers, students, etc."
msgstr ""
"Festius governamentals: un dia especial reconegut per una regió política "
"però sense un dia lliure per a treballadors, estudiants, etc."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:99
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid "Financial Holiday: banks and markets may close on some public holidays"
msgstr ""
"Festiu financer: els bancs i els mercats poden tancar en alguns dies festius "
"oficials"

#: holidaycategories.cpp:102
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Cultural Holiday: a special day in the culture and therefore usually bound "
"to a political region. A day where people celebrate in some fashion. eg. "
"Halloween, St. Valentines"
msgstr ""
"Festa cultural: un dia especial en la cultura i per tant normalment lligat a "
"una regió política. Un dia on la gent celebra d'alguna manera. P. ex. "
"Castanyada, Sant Valentí"

#: holidaycategories.cpp:107
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Commemorative Holiday: a special day to remember usually bound to a "
"political region. Not a day-off from work or school; banks are open, etc."
msgstr ""
"Festius commemoratius: un dia especial per recordar normalment lligat a una "
"regió política. No és un dia lliure del treball o de l'escola; els bancs "
"estan oberts, etc."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:111
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Historical Holiday: similar to a Commemorative Holiday but historical in "
"nature."
msgstr ""
"Festius històrics: similars a una festa commemorativa però de naturalesa "
"històrica."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:114
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Name Day Holiday: in some political regions each day is assigned a first "
"name and persons with that name celebrate that day as their \"Name Day\"."
msgstr ""
"Festius de santoral: en algunes regions polítiques cada dia se li assigna un "
"nom i les persones amb aquest nom celebren aquest dia com el seu «sant»."

#: holidaycategories.cpp:119
msgctxt "QObject|"
msgid ""
"Seasonal Days: the day corresponds to a seasonal event like an equinox, "
"solstice, daylight saving time starts/ends."
msgstr ""
"Dies estacionals: el dia correspon a un esdeveniment estacional com un "
"equinocci, solstici, dia d'inici/final de canvi d'hora."

